snippet.title: Diana and Roma Hogwarts Escape Room Adventure
snippet.description:
Diana Roma Oliver and their parents end up in the Hogwarts Escape Room. After trying to solve the clues, they come up with a plan to get out. Watch as they take on the challenge and find out how they do in this exciting escape room and find their way back to the real world!

If you're a fan of Harry Potter, then you'll love this adventure!

00:00 Diana and Roma Hogwarts Escape Room Adventure
05:55 Diana's Halloween Candy Adventure
13:01 Diana and Roma Overcome Their Fears to Find Oliver
18:16 Oliver and Mom Conquer the 100 Layers Challenge
